      corpus with a cross-model judge keeping the answers honest.
    </p>
    <p class="meta">
      <a href="https://github.com/KucherenkoSerhiy/payments-rag">source →</a>
      <!-- TODO: add live demo URL once the deployment lands -->
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <span class="status wip">◐ scoping</span>
    <h2>llm-cost-gateway</h2>
    <p>
      A gateway between apps and LLM providers: semantic caching, spend tracking, budget
      alerts, provider abstraction.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
